      <title>歌美飒亏损后西门子能源获得 40 亿欧元信贷额度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/siemens-energy-takes-on-4-billion-credit-line-after-gamesa-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西门子能源公司 (Siemens Energy AG) 已获得 40 亿欧元（合 43 亿美元）的信贷额度，用于取代其现有设施以及亏损的歌美飒 (Gamesa) 风力涡轮机部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/siemens-energy-takes-on-4-billion-credit-line-after-gamesa-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Erste 预计风险成本将翻两番，回购 5 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-29/erste-sees-quadrupling-risk-costs-500-million-buyback-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东欧最大的银行第一储蓄银行表示，在经济产出放缓和房地产市场逆风的情况下，预计风险拨备将增加。首席财务官 Stefan Doerfler 在 Daybreak Europe 上与 Tom Mackenzie 就风险削减、净利息收入和股票回购的预期进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-29/erste-sees-quadrupling-risk-costs-500-million-buyback-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:47:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
